      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "THE MIGHTY SPAR (2) has prepared for his return to jumping with three runs on the flat. Has had a trial here since the latest and Pateman sticks aboard from that. This is a suitable assignment. Stablemate LEADERBOARD (1) returns from a spell and concluded the last prep with a win (4500m) at Ballarat, scoring by 25 lengths. Reliable jumper with five wins to his name from 15 appearances and is well placed at best. Expect a bright start to his prep. GOLDEN GARDEN (4) resumes and won his latest jumps trial by a space. Took out a Maiden hurdle three back and looks ready to go. Has claims as well. SAINT EUSTACE (5) has been well-trialled for his return to racing. Wasn't beaten far in a Ballarat steeple when last seen and keep onside.",
